# Commit after execution

Tracked changes from a plan step, agent command, or edit must end in a **git commit** before the work is considered done (unless the user asked not to commit or there are no tracked changes).

- Commit on the branch the user named, else **current branch**; suggest a feature branch when appropriate for risky work.
- Commit only when **build + lints** meet project rules (see SimHub rule / globs for plugin work).
- Message: one line reflecting what shipped.

Cross-ref: [plan-rebase-on-code-changes](.cursor/rules/plan-rebase-on-code-changes.mdc); SimHub **Development cadence** for milestone commits.
